00:27:17,832 --> 00:27:19,834
ALL YOU--
ALL YOU SIMPLY DO IS--

00:27:19,834 --> 00:27:22,403
IS SWING THE SLEEVE IN
WHEN YOU'RE READY TO GO.

00:27:22,403 --> 00:27:24,638
AND AS YOU CAN SEE,
NONE OF 'EM FALL OFF.

00:27:24,638 --> 00:27:27,742
OH, I SEE WHY IT'S WORTH
HALF A MILLION DOLLARS.
THANK YOU!

00:27:27,742 --> 00:27:30,377
IT FOLDS INTO THE COMPUTER.
(sharks laugh)

00:27:30,377 --> 00:27:33,080
OF COURSE THAT MAKES SENSE
TO ME NOW.

