SO FORGET THAT. LET THAT GO.
GIVE ME ANOTHER ONE.

00:28:38,445 --> 00:28:41,348
GIVE ME ANOTHER REASON
WHY THIS IS GREAT.

00:28:41,348 --> 00:28:43,384
