THAT EVERYBODY HAS

00:28:43,384 --> 00:28:45,486
WHO USES STICKY NOTES--
I DON'T HAVE THAT PROBLEM.

00:28:45,486 --> 00:28:48,722
WHO USES STICKY NOTES
WHILE WORKING AT THEIR LAPTOP.

00:28:48,722 --> 00:28:51,492
HAVE YOU SHOWN THIS TO ANYBODY
THAT SAID,

00:28:51,492 --> 00:28:54,495
