OR THE MONEY ON THE PATENT.

00:28:57,965 --> 00:29:02,603
I THINK NO SALES,
A USELESS IDEA. I'M TOTALLY OUT.

00:29:02,603 --> 00:29:05,139
IF YOU
WALKED IN HERE TODAY

00:29:05,139 --> 00:29:07,875
WITH SOME KIND OF INTEREST
IN THIS PRODUCT,

00:29:07,875 --> 00:29:10,744
UH, I THINK YOU MAY BE GETTING
A LITTLE BIT DIFFERENT REACTION

00:29:10,744 --> 00:29:12,713
FROM US RIGHT NOW.
SO I'M OUT.

00:29:12,713 --> 00:29:15,382
