SHE'S HERE WITH A HORRIBLE IDEA
BECAUSE SOMEBODY IN HER FAMILY

00:29:40,768 --> 00:29:42,139
OR HER FRIENDS SAID THAT, TOO.
I'M NOT HER FRIEND.

00:29:42,139 --> 00:29:44,975
"YOU'RE REALLY NICE,"
AND ENCOURAGED YOU.

00:29:44,975 --> 00:29:48,579
HAVE YOU SPENT ANY OF YOUR OWN
MONEY DOING THIS?
I'VE SPENT ABOUT $1,000.

00:29:48,579 --> 00:29:50,815
THAT'S THE GOOD NEWS. YOU SHOULD
STOP. FIND SOMETHING ELSE.

00:29:50,815 --> 00:29:52,817
MOVE ON. I'M OUT.
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

00:29:52,817 --> 00:29:55,453
THANK YOU.
