(laughing)

00:31:33,508 --> 00:31:36,511
WHAT I WANT TO SHOW THE SHARKS
IS THAT THIS IS NOT JUST

00:31:36,511 --> 00:31:38,513
AN AMAZINGLY EFFECTIVE
TEACHING TOOL,

00:31:38,513 --> 00:31:40,982
BUT IT IS AN AMAZING
BUSINESS OPPORTUNITY.

00:31:40,982 --> 00:31:43,985
♪♪

00:31:56,131 --> 00:31:57,632
HELLO, SHARKS.

00:31:57,632 --> 00:31:59,100
MY NAME IS MARC FURIGAY.

00:31:59,100 --> 00:32:01,569
I'M THE CREATOR AND FOUNDER
OF CLASSROOM JAMS--

00:32:01,569 --> 00:32:03,571
AN EDUCATIONAL RECORD LABEL
AND PUBLISHING HOUSE

00:32:03,571 --> 00:32:05,173
SET TO LAUNCH.

00:32:05,173 --> 00:32:10,512
I'M HERE SEEKING $250,000
