WE HAD, KIDS KEPT FAILING,

00:32:21,756 --> 00:32:24,125
AND TEACHERS KEPT BURNING OUT.

00:32:24,125 --> 00:32:26,828
ONE DAY, UH, WHEN I WAS
REALLY STRUGGLING

00:32:26,828 --> 00:32:29,130
TO GET KIDS INTERESTED
IN SHAKESPEARE,

00:32:29,130 --> 00:32:32,000
A STUDENT OF MINE
SUMMED UP THE PROBLEM PERFECTLY.

00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:34,869
